{"id":21,"date":"2019-10-20T22:50:27","date_gmt":"2019-10-20T22:50:27","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/johnsonreviews.com\/?page_id=21"},"modified":"2023-11-19T06:23:51","modified_gmt":"2023-11-19T14:23:51","slug":"about","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/brandonj117.sg-host.com\/about\/","title":{"rendered":"About"},"content":{"rendered":"\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-page\" data-elementor-id=\"21\" class=\"elementor elementor-21\" data-elementor-post-type=\"page\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-2e10ab38 elementor-section-content-middle elementor-reverse-mobile elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"2e10ab38\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-no\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-79a49303\" data-id=\"79a49303\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0a217ab elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"0a217ab\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"512\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP\/\/\/yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7\" data-src=\"https:\/\/brandonj117.sg-host.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/11\/oktoberfest-food-sausage-beer-and-bretzel-1024x512.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-3418 lazyload\" alt=\"Oktoberfest food - sausage, beer and bretzel\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/brandonj117.sg-host.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/11\/oktoberfest-food-sausage-beer-and-bretzel-1024x512.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/brandonj117.sg-host.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/11\/oktoberfest-food-sausage-beer-and-bretzel-300x150.jpg 300w, https:\/\/brandonj117.sg-host.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/11\/oktoberfest-food-sausage-beer-and-bretzel-768x384.jpg 768w, https:\/\/brandonj117.sg-host.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/11\/oktoberfest-food-sausage-beer-and-bretzel-1536x768.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/brandonj117.sg-host.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/11\/oktoberfest-food-sausage-beer-and-bretzel-2048x1024.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><noscript><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"512\" src=\"https:\/\/brandonj117.sg-host.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/11\/oktoberfest-food-sausage-beer-and-bretzel-1024x512.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-3418 lazyload\" alt=\"Oktoberfest food - sausage, beer and bretzel\" srcset=\"https:\/\/brandonj117.sg-host.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/11\/oktoberfest-food-sausage-beer-and-bretzel-1024x512.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/brandonj117.sg-host.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/11\/oktoberfest-food-sausage-beer-and-bretzel-300x150.jpg 300w, https:\/\/brandonj117.sg-host.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/11\/oktoberfest-food-sausage-beer-and-bretzel-768x384.jpg 768w, https:\/\/brandonj117.sg-host.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/11\/oktoberfest-food-sausage-beer-and-bretzel-1536x768.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/brandonj117.sg-host.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/11\/oktoberfest-food-sausage-beer-and-bretzel-2048x1024.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/noscript>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6b2a034d elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"6b2a034d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>In a rapidly evolving world where consumers are more empowered than ever before, their voices, experiences, and opinions are what drive the success and growth of any business. The impetus behind the creation of Johnson Reviews is to give those voices a platform and to offer businesses an insight into the minds of their consumers. We are a company dedicated to conducting unbiased, comprehensive reviews of restaurants and hotels, paired with high-quality ad hoc photography and promotional services.<\/p>\n<p>Founded in 2021, Johnson Reviews is a small but nimble organization with a big vision: to become a leading authority in the hospitality industry. Our team is comprised of seasoned food and travel enthusiasts who possess a deep understanding of the industry and are committed to delivering nothing but authentic, trustworthy, and constructive feedback.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Our Objectives<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Our ultimate goal is to transform the way people make their dining and accommodation decisions by offering them a one-stop platform for unbiased reviews and high-quality visual content. This aim also involves aiding businesses in showcasing their unique offerings and facilitating their continuous improvement through our comprehensive feedback.<\/p>\n<p>Johnson Reviews offers its review services for free, a move designed to maintain the integrity of our reviews while building our reputation and trust with both consumers and businesses. We envision that, with time, our authority in the sector will provide us with a variety of opportunities for monetization, including but not limited to, partnerships, advertising, and consultancy services.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Financial Model<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Our financial model, for now, centers around providing our services free of charge to build trust, authority, and a sizeable audience base. As our reach expands, we plan to monetize our platform through strategic partnerships and advertising. We believe in a win-win situation, where businesses can benefit from our promotional services, and consumers can get an unbiased view of the options available to them. We&#8217;re investing in the future, confident that our revenue will grow exponentially with our influence in the industry.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Conclusion<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>We, at Johnson Reviews, are excited about the road ahead. Despite our small size, we are nimble, passionate, and possess a deep understanding of the potential this industry holds. We are committed to making a significant impact on the way businesses operate and how consumers make choices. While the journey ahead will certainly be filled with challenges, we are confident that our dedicated team, clear vision, and unwavering commitment to our mission will guide us towards our goals. We look forward to shaping the future of the hospitality industry and carving our name as a trusted authority in the field.<\/p>\n<p><!-- notionvc: 28e8d601-1b67-4a7e-8d48-9f9e3565b8e2 --><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-21c48f1 elementor-align-center elementor-widget elementor-widget-button\" data-id=\"21c48f1\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"button.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-button-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-sm elementor-animation-grow\" href=\"\/contact\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-content-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-text\">Contact Us<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>In a rapidly evolving world where consumers are more empowered than ever before, their voices, experiences, and opinions are what &#8230; <a title=\"About\" class=\"r